  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f 9 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd, \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "9 people arrested for trying to find treasure in Vavuniya - scanner, van rescue",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vavuniya police have arrested 9 people yesterday (05.07) evening on charges of trying to search for treasure in Vavuniya Nagar Illupaikulam area and the Vavuniya police have also seized the scanner machine and the van used for the operation.",
        "The Vavuniya Crime Prevention Unit went to the area following a secret information received by the Military Intelligence Unit that there were many suspicious people standing in the area. During this, the police arrested 9 people who were trying to search for the treasure, and the police also seized the van used for transportation and the scanner machine for searching for the treasure.",
        "A 26-year-old person from Nager-Illupaikulam area, a 50-year-old person from Thrumuruppu area, and 9 persons aged 19, 31, 37, 35, 46, 49, 38 from Makara area were arrested.",
        "The Vavunia Police further said that after further investigations of the concerned persons, the suspects, the scanner machine and the vehicle will also be produced in the Vavunia Magistrate's Court."
      ],
